{
  "id": "adv_card_rui_05_03",
  "title": "天動瑠依 3話 私は私のままで",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "おっ、さすがだな。時間に正確だ\nええと、今日は時間を取ってくれてありがとう、っと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ as expected. You're punctual.\nUm‚ thank you for making time today. So‚ um…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1733.3333333,
          "startTime": 6.7333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "あの、{user}さん\nさっきから誰に連絡してるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ {user}-san.\nWho have you been contacting since earlier?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "彼女に頼んでおいたんだ\n天動さんと話をしてほしいって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I asked her to do it.\nI wanted her to talk to Tendo-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.1467902183,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "彼女って……まさか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Her… Could it be…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.209545803,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "チャットなら出来るって、快くOKしてもらえたよ\nこの画面を見てくれ。彼女からのメッセージが届いてる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She gladly agreed‚ saying we can do it through chat.\nTake a look at this screen. I'm receiving a message from her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "ミクからのメッセージですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A message from Miku!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。文字だけのやりとりだけど、伝えてくれ\n天動さんの思っていることを",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. It's only text‚ but tell her everything.\nWhat you're thinking‚ Tendo-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "は、はい！　今日は、突然ごめんなさい\n私、ミクに聞いてほしいことがあるの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "O-Ok! I'm sorry for suddenly asking today.\nThere's something I want to ask Miku.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.9666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5299.999999999997,
          "startTime": 45.7666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "私はミクと違って、他のアイドル達と\n勝ち負けを競い合いながら、歌っている",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Unlike Miku‚\nI sing while competing with other idols‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "ファンのためだけじゃなくて\n自分のため――勝つためにも歌っているの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "not just for the fans' sake‚\nbut also for my own sake—to win.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "それだけじゃない。仲間のため、父のため……\n私の想いは、ミクほど純粋なものじゃないの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And not just that. For the sake of my comrades‚ my father…\nMy feelings are not as pure as Miku's.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "……そんな私の歌が\n人の心を動かすことなんて、出来るのかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I wonder if my songs\ncan truly move people's hearts.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（今、天動さんの悩みを解決出来るのは）\n（鈴村さんや奥山さん、ましてや俺でもない）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Now‚ the one who can solve Tendo-san's worries)\n(It's not Suzumura-san or Okuyama-san‚ much less me)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（俺達とは違う世界で生きてきたミクなんじゃないか）\n（……そんな予感がする）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Isn't it Miku‚ who has lived in a different world from us?)\n(I have a hunch…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.0384594122,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "……あっ、ミクからの返事です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ah‚ it's a reply from Miku.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.6,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_mail-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 97.6
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "「そんな風に、悩んでたんだね\n優しくて真面目な瑠依ちゃんらしいよ」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"So‚ you were troubled like that.\nIt's just like you‚ kind and earnest Rui-chan.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "「でも、私の答えは決まっている\n瑠依ちゃんは、瑠依ちゃんのままでいい」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"But I already have an answer.\nRui-chan‚ it's fine to be yourself.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "「あの日のステージで自分の想いを歌ってもいいって\n教えてくれたのは瑠依ちゃん達、トリエルだよ」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"You taught me that I can sing my own feelings on that day's stage‚\nRui-chan and the others‚ TRINITYAiLE.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03-rui013.m4a",
      "text": "「みんな喜んでくれた、私も嬉しかったし楽しかった\n瑠依ちゃんは、決して間違ってない」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"Everyone was happy‚ and I was happy too.\nRui-chan‚ you're definitely not wrong.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03-rui014.m4a",
      "text": "「お父さんへの気持ち、仲間との絆\nファンへの想い、トップに立ちたいという気持ち」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"Your feelings for your father‚ the bonds with your comrades‚\nyour feelings for the fans‚ and the desire to be at the top.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03-rui015.m4a",
      "text": "「全部まとめて胸に抱いて、ステージに立てばいい」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"Embrace them all in your heart and take the stage.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03-rui016.m4a",
      "text": "「そんな風に、真面目で優しい瑠依ちゃんだから\n私もみんなも、応援したくなるんだよ」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"Because you're earnest and kind like that‚ Rui-chan‚\nboth I and everyone else want to support you.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03-rui017.m4a",
      "text": "「だからその気持ち、全部大切にして下さい」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"So please cherish those feelings‚ all of them.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（……ありがとう、ミク）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(…Thank you‚ Miku)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03-rui018.m4a",
      "text": "この気持ち、全部、大切にしていて……いいの？\n……ありがとう、ミク。私の背中を押してくれて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I should cherish these feelings… all of them?\n…Thank you‚ Miku. You've pushed me forward.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03-rui019.m4a",
      "text": "約束する。私は、私のままで\n必ずトップに立ってみせる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I promise. I will stand at the top‚\nbeing true to myself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03-rui020.m4a",
      "text": "だから、いつかその日が来たら\n――また一緒に歌ってね。さよなら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ when that day comes‚\nlet's sing together again. Goodbye.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 183.8333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "どうだ？　ミクとチャットしてみて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How was it? Chatting with Miku.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 188.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_03-rui021.m4a",
      "text": "はい。もう私は迷いません\n私は、トリエルは、頂点を目指して歌い続けます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. I'm no longer hesitating.\nI will continue to sing‚ aiming for the top with TRINITYAiLE.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 194.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
